Camry.description: It's good looking, feature rich, rides phenomenally and is ultra-efficient thanks to the hybrid system.

Rav4.description: The 2015 Toyota RAV4 is a compact crossover slotting under the midsize Venza. It is available with a 2.5-liter I-4 with 176 hp and 172 lb-ft of torque paired to a six-speed automatic transmission in all-wheel drive configurations.

Civic.description: The 2017 Honda Civic comes standard with a 158-horsepower, 2.0-liter four-cylinder engine, a six-speed manual transmission and front-wheel drive. Exterior highlights include 16-inch wheels and LED daytime running lights and taillights.

6.description: The Mazda 6 is a front wheel drive 4 door with 5 seats, powered by a 2.5L INLINE 4 engine that has 140 kW of power (at 6000 rpm) and 252 Nm of torque (at 4000 rpm) via a Six-speed Automatic.

CX9.description: The CX-9 is an all wheel drive 4 door with 7 seats, powered by a 2.5L TURBO 4 engine that has 170 kW of power (at 5000 rpm) and 420 Nm of torque (at 2000 rpm) via a Six-speed Automatic.

Yaris.description: The Yaris is a front wheel drive 5 door with 5 seats, powered by a 1.3L INLINE 4 engine that has 63 kW of power (at 6000 rpm) and 121 Nm of torque (at 4400 rpm) via a Four-speed Automatic

cr-v.description: The CR-V is a front wheel drive 4 door with 5 seats, powered by a 1.5L TURBO 4 engine that has 140 kW of power (at 5600 rpm) and 240 Nm of torque (at 2000 rpm) via a Continuous Variable.

forester.description: The Forester is an all wheel drive 4 door with 5 seats, powered by a 2.5L INLINE 4 engine that has 136 kW of power (at 5800 rpm) and 239 Nm of torque (at 4400 rpm) via a Continuous Variable.

GT-R.description: The 2020 GT-R's standard twin-turbo 3.8-liter V-6 makes a mighty 565 horsepower. It hooks up to a six-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel drive that conspire to put all that power to the pavement.

Phantom.description: The Phantom is a rear wheel drive 4 door with 5 seats, powered by a 6.7L V12 engine that has 420 kW of power (at 5000 rpm) and 900 Nm of torque (at 1700 rpm) via an Eight-speed Automatic.

Q5.description: The base Q5 features 18-inch wheels with chubby tyres, leather trim, a powered tailgate, reversing camera, front and rear parking sensors and Xenon headlamps.
